            class="- topic/topic concept/concept ">
		    <title class="- topic/title ">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">13.105</ph> Synopsis and posting requirements.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
			      <ol id="d733e13" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d747e17" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The contracting officer must comply with the public display and synopsis requirements of <xref href="FAR-i1120993.dita#i1120993"
                        base="i1120993"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">5.101</xref> and <xref href="FAR-i1120755.dita#i1120755"
                        base="i1120755"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">5.203</xref> unless an exception in <xref href="FAR-i1120688.dita#i1120688"
                        base="i1120688"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">5.202</xref> applies.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d747e35" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            When acquiring commercial items or supplies or services procured in accordance with 12.102(f)(1), the contracting officer may use a combined synopsis and solicitation. In these cases, a separate solicitation is not required. The contracting officer must include enough information to permit suppliers to develop quotations or offers.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d747e44" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            See <xref href="FAR-i1121037.dita#i1121037"
                        base="i1121037"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">5.102</xref>(a)(6) for the requirement to post a brand name justification or documentation required by <xref href="FAR-i1112291.dita#i1112291"
                        base="i1112291"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">13.106-1</xref>(b) or <xref href="FAR-i1111284.dita#i1111284"
                        base="i1111284"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">13.501</xref>.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d747e62" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            When publicizing contract actions funded in whole or in part by the American Recovery and Reinvestment Act of 2009 (Pub. L. 111-5):</p>
					          <ol id="d733e68" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d747e72" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Notices of proposed contract actions shall follow the procedures in <xref href="FAR-i1120239.dita#i1120239"
                              base="i1120239"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">5.704</xref> for posting orders.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d747e84" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Award notices shall follow the procedures in <xref href="FAR-i1120260.dita#i1120260"
                              base="i1120260"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">5.705</xref>.</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
			      </ol>
